<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/claire-hughes--2> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Claire Hughes was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Wales Office and Assistant Whip, House of Commons on 16 September 2025. She was previously Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) between 7 September 2025 and 16 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Bangor Aberconwy in July 2024."@en .
